example:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;config.getURL(&quot;test.myservice-1..0&quot;);&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This has been fixed in the upcoming 1.2 release, you can give a try at the&lt;br/&gt;
latest release candidate:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://people.apache.org/~oheger/commons-configuration-1.2RC3&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://people.apache.org/~oheger/commons-configuration-1.2RC3&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;


