&amp;gt; Hi Luis, in this case you have to use the double dot syntax in your keys, for&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;gt; example:&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;gt; &lt;br/&gt;
&amp;gt; config.getURL(&quot;test.myservice-1..0&quot;);&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;gt; &lt;br/&gt;
&amp;gt; This has been fixed in the upcoming 1.2 release, you can give a try at the&lt;br/&gt;
