&amp;gt; *** This bug has been marked as a duplicate of 35509 ***&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Cool.&lt;br/&gt;
I would have gone with the backslash notation though, as described in 35509.&lt;br/&gt;
At any rate, this should also be documented in the XML Howto.&lt;br/&gt;
Thanks.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
